-- **PostgreSQL** runs on the internal Docker network only (no DB port published to the host by default).
-- **Uploads** persist in volume `educycle_uploads` → `/app/data/uploads` in the API container.
+- `POSTGRES_PASSWORD`
+- `JWT_SECRET`
 
